Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.21,0:01:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.54,0:01:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開那孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.38,0:01:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左臉的十字傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.45,0:01:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你就是\N大名鼎鼎的緋村劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.32,0:02:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也是來搶赤空最後的名刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.79,0:02:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要的是別的刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.29,0:02:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要赤空的刀就要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.43,0:02:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你要先把那孩子放了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.16,0:02:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第四十話\N可怕的無情刺客\N十本刀和張的死鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.80,0:02:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不必為了一個孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.27,0:02:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大打出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.74,0:02:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的逆刃刀已斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.68,0:02:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已沒有武器可決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.85,0:02:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要打敗你是輕而易舉的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.08,0:02:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不必打就已分出勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.82,0:02:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就替志志雄殺了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.99,0:02:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.49,0:02:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好不容易拿到一把上乘好劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.83,0:02:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我試試它的威力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.17,0:02:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就從你開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.90,0:02:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,試試殺小孩的滋味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.81,0:03:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.91,0:03:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就來場正大光明的決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.18,0:03:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的劍已斷  你又挾有人質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.05,0:03:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣子叫什麼正大光明決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.72,0:03:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就隨便你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.99,0:03:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.56,0:03:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看看你有多厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.67,0:03:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你能打贏我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.90,0:03:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就可以打贏齊藤的牙突劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.84,0:03:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.21,0:03:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不再考慮清楚嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.25,0:03:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的刀已斷  絕對打不贏我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.99,0:03:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會後悔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.06,0:03:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這把就是赤空打的殺人奇劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.03,0:03:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.49,0:03:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人體若被此劍所傷\N若不即時治療
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.07,0:03:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傷口將會腐爛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.74,0:04:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.31,0:04:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到你還是執迷不悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.42,0:04:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再忍耐一下  我馬上救你下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.23,0:04:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說放下就放下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.60,0:04:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你把我張某當成什麼人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.54,0:04:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.27,0:04:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊織 再忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.98,0:04:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是存心跟我過不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.21,0:04:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧 就讓你看看我的厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.86,0:04:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼招式儘管使出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.23,0:04:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別儘是些不中用的花樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.23,0:04:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是要開始來真的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.77,0:05:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸  快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.70,0:05:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道緋村怎樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.27,0:05:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猜也沒用  我們到了就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.27,0:05:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村的劍已經斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.14,0:05:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爺爺你真小氣\N也不借他一把劍用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.68,0:05:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要亂講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.75,0:05:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了 他們開始打起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.35,0:05:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村這傢伙真是沉不住氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.02,0:05:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要不用刀決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.86,0:05:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村就不會輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.29,0:05:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.00,0:05:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心那男人身上的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.93,0:05:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是家父赤空改良的\N後期型殺人奇劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.11,0:05:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我張十刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.68,0:05:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在要開始出招了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.18,0:05:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看招了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.38,0:05:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.78,0:05:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙帶了刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.45,0:05:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我的愛刀 殺人奇劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.02,0:05:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄刃乃太刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.62,0:06:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.56,0:06:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差一點  就打到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.50,0:06:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算你好運  這次我不會放過你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.30,0:06:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺人奇劍  薄刃乃太刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.84,0:06:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是一把極薄極鋒利的刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.51,0:06:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以快速自由變幻招式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.21,0:06:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真令人捏把冷汗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.25,0:06:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果被那把薄刃乃太刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.22,0:06:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,砍到的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.89,0:06:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼時候多出了看好戲的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.66,0:06:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想死的人就快滾到一邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.49,0:06:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.53,0:06:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打不贏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.20,0:06:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.23,0:06:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸的劍 放棄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.64,0:06:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看我的大蛇劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.81,0:06:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管不了了  救伊織要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.11,0:06:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他現在正專心決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.24,0:06:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,注意力沒有在這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.28,0:06:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利用這個時候救伊織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.52,0:07:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.02,0:07:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想害死緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.39,0:07:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你明知他現在處於下風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.06,0:07:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你小心了我要上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.86,0:07:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒打完呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.10,0:07:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙緊迫盯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.07,0:07:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.64,0:07:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我又沒有叫他決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.37,0:07:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是他自己要決鬥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.81,0:07:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你救子心切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.12,0:07:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村現在是為了誰而戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.59,0:07:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你忘了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.32,0:07:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.86,0:07:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不知死活的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.13,0:07:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個小鬼的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.80,0:07:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,值得你這麼做嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.17,0:07:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對你來說他是小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.64,0:08:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但對我來說\N他是無可取代的新生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.28,0:08:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你快把伊織放了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.52,0:08:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼革命家的自大論調
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.23,0:08:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的時代已經結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.53,0:08:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在是志志雄的時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.66,0:08:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我的薄刀乃太刀的時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.97,0:08:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你安心受死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.70,0:08:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來你真是執迷不悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.64,0:08:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.81,0:08:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創造時代的不是刀劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.31,0:08:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是擁有刀劍的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.88,0:08:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別再廢話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.72,0:08:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快納命來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.52,0:08:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.42,0:08:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.06,0:08:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這看好戲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.26,0:08:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,存心來找死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.13,0:08:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.57,0:08:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,青空  快把伊織帶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.61,0:09:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下伊織  我來救你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.31,0:09:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.28,0:09:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,青空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.75,0:09:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知死活的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.62,0:09:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.08,0:09:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先父以製造刀劍\N來創造新時代的用意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.19,0:09:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.36,0:09:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要被他溜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.96,0:09:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.96,0:09:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創造新時代的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.76,0:09:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.96,0:09:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能夠守護和平的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.63,0:09:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧 就托付給此人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.17,0:09:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將父親的最後一把刀\N交給這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.88,0:09:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和伊織一定要守護\N這個和平的新時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.85,0:09:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.45,0:09:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是交差攻法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.75,0:09:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村沒刀怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.72,0:09:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後的一擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.66,0:09:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果輸的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.86,0:10:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙還是不死心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.17,0:10:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看你還能撐到什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.04,0:10:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次我不會再放過你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.34,0:10:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了  勝算不大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.44,0:10:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果有刀就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.61,0:10:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.95,0:10:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是家父的最後一把刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.82,0:10:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你使用它吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.26,0:10:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是赤空的名刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.03,0:10:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛好利用這個機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.53,0:10:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好見識一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.87,0:10:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這把刀還是那把刀厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.11,0:10:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.94,0:10:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上了  緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.54,0:10:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有了刀你就贏定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.22,0:10:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.55,0:10:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.75,0:11:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村不能拔刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.59,0:11:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村已立下誓言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.69,0:11:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不再使用\N逆刃刀以外的劍殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.07,0:11:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都什麼時候  還管這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.14,0:11:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在如果他不殺人就會被殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.61,0:11:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果緋村用了這把刀殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.04,0:11:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他就要重新恢復殺手的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.85,0:11:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.15,0:11:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是殺手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.02,0:11:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後他就無法再成為普通人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.89,0:11:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個殺手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.77,0:11:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還在發什麼呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.04,0:11:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你忘記怎麼殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.01,0:11:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來教你好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.24,0:11:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就表演給你看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.25,0:11:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.88,0:12:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就拿這個你所謂的新生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.05,0:12:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,示範給你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.84,0:12:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,膽小鬼發威了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.80,0:12:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別上他的圈套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.77,0:12:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看老子怎麼加倍還給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.08,0:12:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒用的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.94,0:12:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我從後面解決你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.88,0:12:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.25,0:12:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼招勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.19,0:12:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從哪學來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.22,0:12:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流 龍卷閃旋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.12,0:13:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解決了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.67,0:14:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.65,0:14:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.52,0:14:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.63,0:14:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村  你看這把刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.57,0:15:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.34,0:15:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到赤空打的最後一把刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.47,0:15:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟是逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.88,0:15:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.12,0:15:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.99,0:15:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒有殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.56,0:15:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一向只打殺人劍的父親\N會在最後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.30,0:15:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煉了一把逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.94,0:15:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.07,0:15:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這支白木柄\N居然能耐得住緋村的力道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.38,0:15:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.61,0:15:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斬我千銀髮  煉刀幾星霜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.48,0:15:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖為子孫恨  但為後代福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.75,0:16:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赤空花費畢生之精力\N打造了這些劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.83,0:16:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己雖得承受被兒子憎恨的可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.46,0:16:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但卻能給後代子孫造福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.17,0:16:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可能是赤空去世前\N刻下的詩句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.31,0:16:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是父親有所覺悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.28,0:16:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原本家父為自己的鑄刀功力深以為傲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.01,0:16:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本以為只要有刀劍\N就可創造和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.28,0:16:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到事實與現實剛好相反
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.82,0:16:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此父親心中充滿了\N深深的悔恨與希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.89,0:16:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再次打造了這把御神刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.69,0:16:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.93,0:16:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再次打造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.60,0:16:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父親打御神刀時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.10,0:16:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事先就打造了二把
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.84,0:16:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼這把就是第二把逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.94,0:16:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這把是比逆刃刀\N更厲害的逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.18,0:16:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你收下吧  緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.48,0:17:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完成先父的遺志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.15,0:17:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是個志士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.29,0:17:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在好不容易\N才剛打勝鳥羽伏見之仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.33,0:17:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎能就此罷手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.63,0:17:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你洗手不幹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.33,0:17:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以後想做什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.53,0:17:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赤空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.14,0:17:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從今以後 我不再殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.50,0:17:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只要保護好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.11,0:17:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我身邊的人就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.44,0:17:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果世事像你所想的就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.38,0:17:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界上就不會有那麼多壞人殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.68,0:17:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼多好人被殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.12,0:17:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你真的已作此決定了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.72,0:17:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.16,0:17:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許你不再需要刀劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.96,0:17:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姑且你就帶這把刀在身上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.17,0:17:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許它能幫你實現自己的志願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.11,0:17:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果有一天刀斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.04,0:17:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還需要一把好刀時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.88,0:18:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就來京都找我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.65,0:18:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我又回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.62,0:18:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赤空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.19,0:18:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切如你所料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.93,0:18:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你為我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.69,0:18:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打了一把新的逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.20,0:18:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.03,0:18:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔再見  叔叔再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.16,0:18:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們來京都都三天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.49,0:18:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼都沒見到劍心的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.93,0:18:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別自作主張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.93,0:18:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個人到街上亂找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.90,0:18:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.17,0:18:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.97,0:19:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別小看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.31,0:19:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會幫你找到劍心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.08,0:19:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別亂來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.21,0:19:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正我有的是時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.31,0:19:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我上街逛逛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.82,0:19:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞不好會遇到劍心也不一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.72,0:19:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是四乃森蒼紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.63,0:19:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在這幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.60,0:19:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡  不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.63,0:19:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彌彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.70,0:19:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看那傢伙賊頭賊腦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.01,0:19:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道又想找劍心什麼麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.07,0:19:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.34,0:19:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,張十刀已被警察帶走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.28,0:19:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是比古清十郎的地址
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.02,0:19:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想這地方可能不太好找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.46,0:19:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.03,0:19:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是非去不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.99,0:19:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿操就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.40,0:20:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫的事我幫不上忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.53,0:20:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.60,0:20:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.94,0:20:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.44,0:20:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會忘記你的  緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.01,0:20:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也別忘記我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.28,0:20:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.95,0:20:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村  馬上要吃飯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.75,0:20:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下  你上哪去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.16,0:20:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又要上哪去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.46,0:20:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想再給你們添麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.30,0:20:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就此道別了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.87,0:20:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也不必這麼快就走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.97,0:20:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不管你是不是殺手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.51,0:20:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不是有使命要去完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.58,0:20:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只知道你是緋村劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.22,0:20:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我們的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.49,0:20:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼好笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.59,0:20:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在東京的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.52,0:21:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也有人跟我說過同樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.36,0:21:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到到了京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.60,0:21:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我又聽到你這樣說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.80,0:21:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.54,0:21:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.61,0:21:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.38,0:21:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村不只是個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.78,0:21:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心地善良的青年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.71,0:21:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也是個有理想有正義感的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.15,0:21:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望他這次去能夠平安無事
